    • Method Detail

      • addSupportedCredentialType

        public CredentialCallback.Builder addSupportedCredentialType(Class<? extends Credential> credentialType)
        Add a credential type to be supported by the CredentialCallback. The specified credential type is considered supported for all algorithms.
        Parameters:
        credentialType - the supported Credential type.
        Returns:
        This CredentialCallback.Builder to allow additional types to be added.

      • addSupportedCredentialType

        public CredentialCallback.Builder addSupportedCredentialType(Class<? extends Credential> credentialType,
                                                             String... supportedAlgorithms)
        Add a credential type to be supported by the CredentialCallback along with the list of algorithms it is supported with.
        Parameters:
        credentialType - credentialType the supported Credential type.
        supportedAlgorithms - the names of the algorithms the credential type is supported with.
        Returns:
        This CredentialCallback.Builder to allow additional types to be added.

      • build

        public CredentialCallback build()
        Build the CredentialCallback with the set of supported credential types added to this builder. Once this builder is built no further modifications are allowed.
        Returns:
        The CredentialCallback with the set of supported credential types added to this builder.
